{"type":"answer","id":323393,"parentType":"question","parentId":29822,"uid":2296,"contents":"窝个人建议以 f(x)=floor(ln(x)+1)来点餐，这样子的点餐方式可以保证一个人也有菜吃，但是f(x)的导数是持续小于一的，考虑到人饭量的边际递减效应。（floor function指向下取整函数，又为E(x)=max{n in Z|n&lt;=x}）<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Wtfx1cX.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Wtfx1cX.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Wtfx1cX.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-08-15","agreeCount":47,"discussionCount":7}